âœ… Definition: A package is a namespace that groups related classes, interfaces, and sub-packages for better organization and access control.

âœ… Types of Packages:
	1.	Built-in Packages (e.g., java.util, java.io, java.lang)
	2.	User-Defined Packages (Custom packages created by developers)

âœ… Declaring a Package:
	â€¢	First line in a Java file:

